  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Constrict",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon attacks a target with its tail that is Medium or smaller, aiming to&nbsp;deal 4/W3. If hit, the target must make a TN 5 Prowess saving throw. If they fail, they become fully&nbsp;Restrained by the demon&rsquo;s tail. The Restrained target will take a 4/W3 Wound at the beginning of its&nbsp;turn. For each subsequent turn Restrained, the damage increases by 2. The restraint can be broken&nbsp;by succeeding on a contested Exertion check. If the demon decides it doesn't want to restrain them&nbsp;any longer, it can release them at any time on its turn for free. Killing the demon will also release&nbsp;the hold.</p>",
        "action": "major"
      },
