    {
      "name": "Undead",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon is extremely hard to kill. Calculate what it&rsquo;s Wound Threshold&nbsp;should be according to the rules on page 37, and multiply that number by 3. That is this demon&rsquo;s&nbsp;Wound Threshold. When it is dropped to 0 Hitpoints while at or below its Wound Threshold, it will&nbsp;appear dead to anything less than thorough inspection. It will revive in minutes, clearing enough&nbsp;Wounds to recover to half HP, starting with the least severe. It will continue this until actually killed.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
      },
